Never thought I would post about this incident ! I might even delete the video later .

I hardly mentioned 10% of what she has done to destroy my dream . 

Did she get what she deserved ? I dont know 

I dont hate her , may be I had everything that she wanted to have in life . 

I hope she changes for her own good & I hope to make peace with everthing she has done. 

Am I alright now ? I dont know . The entire incident still haunts me.

A special thanks to @karthik_naniii , for the immense support and all my other staff who stood with me , who came to P.S inspite of being “women” !

latestPosts.caption:
We are initiating strict and uncompromising legal action.
This includes influencers, YouTubers, meme pages or individuals who contributed to this damage - directly or indirectly.
The law will take its course, and truth will stand tall in the end.
We are not here to play the social media game.
We are here to protect what we built with our sweat, and integrity.

To Our Friends & HK family,

The last 25 days have tested us deeply.
We were thrown into a storm of false allegations, memes, and manipulation, without even being given a fair chance to share our truth.
When we tried to speak, our organic voice was silenced - crushed under the weight of a calculated PR attack.
But today, we finally spoke our truth.
In a press meet attended by over 50 reputed media channels, we addressed every question with honesty, clarity, and transparency.
We have also begun submitting all evidence and documents to the DGP and other higher authorities to support our stand.
To those who stood by us, believed in us thankyou, we owe you our strength ❤️🫂 

- Team HK

latestPosts.caption: Celebrating our 5th wedding anniversary fills my heart with immense joy and gratitude, as I reflect on the beautiful journey we have shared together. From the moment we got married my life  has been filled with unwavering love, support, and countless cherished memories. Each day with you has been a testament to the strength of our bond, the laughter we have shared, and the dreams we have built together. Your kindness, patience, and unwavering love have been my constant source of strength and happiness. As we celebrate this special milestone, I am reminded of how blessed I am to have you as my partner, my confidant, and my best friend. Here’s to many more years of love, laughter, and shared adventures. Happy anniversary, my love!

Over years you guys have been showering us with so much love and kindness that we always wanted to give back the same love in some or the other way.. 
Thankyou sooo much to our loyal insta fam ❤️🫂🧿

latestPosts.caption:
Some moments are so overwhelming that you forget to pause and capture them… just like @hk.hospitals launch day
Woke up at 5 a.m. with so much excitement for the inauguration of HK Hospitals, and once the event began, I got completely lost in the laughter, blessings, and love of my family and friends.
It was only around 8 p.m. that I realized — I hadn’t taken a single solo picture!
But somehow, I gathered the last bit of my energy because I truly wanted to capture this special day, in this beautiful saree designed by @tasyacouture 
Mittu, you made me feel so, so beautiful — thank you from the bottom of my heart!
This day marks not just the opening of a hospital, but a dream turned into reality, from a vision to something that will touch so many lives. 

Forever grateful, forever hustling, forever dreaming.
HK is not just a name — it’s a story of passion, purpose, and perseverance.
Here’s to new beginnings, and to many more milestones ahead!

Saree : @tasyacouture 
Makeup and hair : @makeup_artistry_by_jeevani
